		<div class="entry" id="entry-6a00d8341c630a53ef0133f2932c29970b">
	
	<h1 class="entry-header"><a href="/web/20100817183527/http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/comments_blog/2010/07/lindsay-lohan-wont-be-released-this-week.html" rel="bookmark" title="Lindsay Lohan won't be released this week; readers deliver a mixed judgement">Lindsay Lohan won't be released this week; readers deliver a mixed judgement</a></h1>
	
	
<div class="time" style="margin-bottom:8px;">July 26, 2010&nbsp;|&nbsp;<span style="color:#8b0412;font-size:130%"> 3:38</span>
<span style="color:#8b0412">pm</span></div>
	
	<div class="entry-content">
	<div class="entry-body clearfix">
	<p><a href="/web/20100817183527/http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/.a/6a00d8341c630a53ef0133f2932de1970b-pi" style="float: right;"><img alt="Lindsay Lohan on her way to Lynwood Detention Facility" class="asset asset-image at-xid-6a00d8341c630a53ef0133f2932de1970b " src="/web/20100817183527im_/http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/.a/6a00d8341c630a53ef0133f2932de1970b-320wi" style="width: 320px; margin: 0px 0px 5px 5px;" title="Lindsay Lohan on her way to Lynwood Detention Facility" /></a>Everyone&#39;s favorite incarcerated starlet, <a href="/web/20100817183527/http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/lanow/2010/07/lindsay-lohan-will-not-be-released-from-jail-this-week-sheriffs-official-says.html">Lindsay Lohan, won&#39;t be leaving</a> Lynwood’s Century Regional Detention Facility this week as some have speculated.</p><p>Even though the actress was sentenced to 90 days in the hole, because of jail overcrowding, non-violent criminals like Lohan typically only have to serve a fraction of that behind bars. On Monday, the L.A. County Sheriff&#39;s Department let it be known that this would not be the week that the &quot;Mean Girls&quot; star will breathe the fresh air of freedom.</p><p>&quot;She won&#39;t be released this week,&quot; said Steve Whitmore, a Sheriff’s Department spokesman.</p><p>Readers of LA Now were both thrilled and disappointed by the latest LiLo news, and several compared the actress to another famous former inmate, Paris Hilton.</p><p><a href="/web/20100817183527/http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/lanow/2010/07/lindsay-lohan-will-not-be-released-from-jail-this-week-sheriffs-official-says.html?cid=6a00d8341c630a53ef0133f291a481970b#comment-6a00d8341c630a53ef0133f291a481970b">liz said</a>: <span id="comment-6a00d8341c630a53ef0133f291a481970b-content">For pete&#39;s
 sake, she learned her lesson, she is a much better human being that 
Paris Hilton. She&#39;s trying so hard to fight the evil that keeps 
dragging her down. Just let her go.</span></p><p><span id="comment-6a00d8341c630a53ef013485b6a3ff970c-content"><a href="/web/20100817183527/http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/lanow/2010/07/lindsay-lohan-will-not-be-released-from-jail-this-week-sheriffs-official-says.html?cid=6a00d8341c630a53ef013485b6a3ff970c#comment-6a00d8341c630a53ef013485b6a3ff970c">David fired back</a>: The 
standard is whether she&#39;s better than Paris? Then we should probably 
release a lot of folks in there who, if they had had Paris&#39; advantages, 
would have been good solid citizens.</span></p><p><a href="/web/20100817183527/http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/lanow/2010/07/lindsay-lohan-will-not-be-released-from-jail-this-week-sheriffs-official-says.html?cid=6a00d8341c630a53ef013485b63abf970c#comment-6a00d8341c630a53ef013485b63abf970c">Turkish Yogurt wrote</a>: <span id="comment-6a00d8341c630a53ef013485b63abf970c-content">I hope the young people out there learn something from this.</span></p><p><span id="comment-6a00d8341c630a53ef013485b63abf970c-content"><a href="/web/20100817183527/http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/lanow/2010/07/lindsay-lohan-will-not-be-released-from-jail-this-week-sheriffs-official-says.html?cid=6a00d8341c630a53ef0133f2919e80970b#comment-6a00d8341c630a53ef0133f2919e80970b">phoenixandrew said</a>: </span><span id="comment-6a00d8341c630a53ef0133f2919e80970b-content">I doubt 
Lindsay will have learned anything from her short stint in jail, nor 
will she be any different when she gets out. She just doesn&#39;t get it.</span></p><p><span id="comment-6a00d8341c630a53ef0133f2919e80970b-content"><a href="/web/20100817183527/http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/lanow/2010/07/lindsay-lohan-will-not-be-released-from-jail-this-week-sheriffs-official-says.html?cid=6a00d8341c630a53ef0133f2926bcf970b#comment-6a00d8341c630a53ef0133f2926bcf970b">James said</a>: </span><span id="comment-6a00d8341c630a53ef0133f2926bcf970b-content">overcrowding?
 then eliminate those on death row and problem solved. No 
overcrowding, less money for taxpayers taking care of prisoners. But 
maybe its just me.</span></p><p><span id="comment-6a00d8341c630a53ef0133f2926bcf970b-content">So what&#39;s your take?&#0160; Will a few days in jail help to rehabilitate Lohan and stop her from making reckless choices? Or did the jail do the right thing by incarcerating her for a few more days? Or do you believe that even though she was a non-violent offender that she should do the full 90-day sentence?</span></p><p><span id="comment-6a00d8341c630a53ef0133f2926bcf970b-content">Share your thoughts in the comments below.</span></p><p><span id="comment-6a00d8341c630a53ef0133f2926bcf970b-content">-- Tony Pierce</span></p><em>Photo: Confetti flies as Lindsay Lohan arrives at 
the Beverly Hills courthouse in Beverly Hills last week. Credit: AP Photo / Reed Saxon <br /></em><p></p><p><a href="/web/20100817183527/http://www.latimes.com/news/local/la-me-lohan-jail-pictures,0,549900.photogallery"><img src="/web/20100817183527im_/http://www.latimes.com/media/thumbnails/photogallery/2010-07/55057072-20102327.jpg" /></a></p>
<p><strong>Photos:</strong> <a href="/web/20100817183527/http://www.latimes.com/news/local/la-me-lohan-jail-pictures,0,549900.photogallery">Lindsay Lohan ordered to jail</a></p>

<p><a href="/web/20100817183527/http://www.latimes.com/news/local/la-et-bio-llohan-pg,0,777281.photogallery"><img alt="" src="/web/20100817183527im_/http://www.latimes.com/media/thumbnails/photogallery/2010-06/31400158-30183537.jpg" /></a></p>
<p><strong>Photos:</strong> <a href="/web/20100817183527/http://www.latimes.com/news/local/la-et-bio-llohan-pg,0,777281.photogallery">Lindsay Lohan life in pictures </a></p>
	</div>
	
